Dad for Father's Day: a big, juicy barbecued sausage that tastes
good or a healthy grilled plantain that is good for him? The
decision is not easy for Steven Raichlen, the author of The
Barbecue Bible and Healthy Latin Cooking, both of which have won
1999 national cookbook awards. (Rice, Austin American-Statesman).
</P>
