<DOCNO> NYT19990609.0074 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-09 10:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8514 &Cx1f; tad-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NEWS-QUESTIONS10-TAKE     06-09 1530
