of his films on video, including ``The Lady Vanishes,'' ``North by
Northwest,'' ``The Birds,'' ``Foreign Correspondent,'' ``Shadow of
a Doubt'' and Hitchcock's only best picture winner ``Rebecca.''
(BLongino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 24.
