</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    RATINGS OF FILMS, OTHER MEDIA NOT RELIABLE, CRITICS CHARGE
 &HT;    1160&AMP;trim. With RATINGS-DATA. Moving in (w) Washington and (e)
entertainment categories.
