<HEADLINE>
`SMART' MICROWAVES THAT READ THE INSTRUCTIONS ON THE PACKAGE 
</HEADLINE>
   (Circuits)  
(ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.) 
(Eds: Also moving in `a' category.) 
(jt) 
 By LISA GUERNSEY    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
