<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-09 17:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9094 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-POWERS-SPYFILMS-840(2     06-09 0677
