made the promise in a letter to Grover Norquist of the influential
Americans for Tax Reform of Washington. ``I will oppose and veto
any increase in individual or corporate marginal income tax rates
or individual or corporate income tax hikes,'' Bush wrote. By JAY
ROOT. Story has moved in ``a'' general news category. &QL; 
