<P>
   JOKES
</P>
<P>
   Q: Where do cows go on dates?
</P>
<P>
   A: To the mooovies! _ Jordan Ray Hiler.
</P>
<P>
   Q: What is the key to Thanksgiving?
</P>
<P>
   A: A turkey. _ Garrett Myer.
</P>
<P>
